  defaultText: 'I''m having the most fun! And I''m sure it would go just fine! I
    have been riding waves for just about my entire life so.... I''d like to think
    I can probably pull it off!  let''s... start with the sandwiches though! If you
    don''t eat first, you''ll end up eating sand! '
